===Main drops===

The probability for a player to receive a [[mithril ore]] drop depends on the player's mining level. The rock will deplete after receiving the mithril ore, unless affected by the effect of [[Superior mining gloves|superior]] or [[Expert mining gloves|expert mining gloves]].

{{DropsTableHead}}
{{DropsLineSkill|name=Mithril ore|quantity=1|rarity=Always|skill=Mining}}
{{DropsTableBottom}}

The chance of successfully mining a mithril rock varies from 4/256 at level 1 (if such a thing were possible), up to 50/256 at level 99.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1407009871564840964|quote=Mithril: 1.6% - 19.6%.|date=21 June 2021|archiveurl=https://archive.is/V0eDD|archivedate=21 June 2021}}

